OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely dry
OL,6,Fthis evening with plenty of late
OL,7,Fsunshine, although some cloud may
OL,8,Faffect coastal areas at times. Little
OL,9,Fchange overnight, with clear spells
OL,10,Fallowing patchy mist to form.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA largely fine day to come
OL,13,Fwith a mix of sunshine and some cloud
OL,14,Fbubbling up at times. feeling hot in
OL,15,Fthe sunshine, although feel a little
OL,16,Fcooler near coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
