OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FRemaining largely dry, sunny and hot
OL,7,Fthroughout. A few showers possible
OL,8,Flater Friday and Saturday but most
OL,9,Fstaying dry. Light winds initially but
OL,10,Fa freshening easterly breeze
OL,11,Fdeveloping by Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
